COSIMO REGA PUBLISHED THE BOOK

882
01:09:35,039 --> 01:09:37,200
SUMIWON 'O FALCO
AUTOBIOGRAPHY OF A LIFER

883
01:09:38,000 --> 01:09:39,760
SALVATORE STRIANO
WAS PARDONED,

884
01:09:39,840 --> 01:09:41,800
AND NOW ACTS
IN THEATRE AND FILMS

885
